=============
== General ==
=============
 
This package provides a tests for the grid tools used with the LHCb experiment. The individual tests are located in the directory "./tests/<package>" and are written in python.unittest style.

====================
== Invoking tests ==
====================

Tests can be invoked in two styles, either each file can be individually run via python.unittest, e.g. from the root directory run

_________________________________________________________________________________

python tests/castor/test_castor_cli.py 
..
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Ran 2 tests in 0.095s

OK
_________________________________________________________________________________


or tests can be run via nose, e.g.

_________________________________________________________________________________

[pcites03] /afs/cern.ch/user/r/roiser/w0/work/grid-unit-tests > nosetests tests/
..
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Ran 2 tests in 0.102s

OK
